    printf("enter a string\n");
  gets(a);
    printf("the string  is ");
    puts(a);

    
    
    return 0;
}

enter a string
geeks for geeks
the string is geeks for geeks


getch    is used to entre a character ,it wont be displayed on screen and it will go to next line without prerssing og entre
getchar is used to entre a character ,it will be displayed on screen and it willnot go to next line without prerssing  entre
